const hexToRgb = hex =>
            hex.replace(/^#?([a-f\d])([a-f\d])([a-f\d])$/i
                , (m, r, g, b) => '#' + r + r + g + g + b + b)
                .substring(1).match(/.{2}/g)
                .map(x => parseInt(x, 16))
